{
  "texts": [
    "a For a fair comparison, the \"direct learning\" results without any extra input are compared. b",
    "The best results are reported among four variants of GemNet and four orders l ∈ {0, 1, 2, 3} of NequIP.",
    "The number of training splits is the same as sGDML.",
    "ViSNet-improper contains the runtime improper calculation in the ViS-MP.",
    "The best one in each category is highlighted in bold."
  ]
}